---
title: Chicken Stroganoff with Savoury Rice and Peas
description: Our take on this classic Russian recipe is a chicken dinner the whole family will fall in love with. The tangy, creamy sauce pairs beautifully with broth-flavoured rice, too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-stroganoff-014309d0.jpg
